{"tid":145409,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄足總官員倡辦球迷打鬥世界盃","createTime":"2017-03-06T08:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T01:34:28.000Z","uid":5195,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dfd64bd4bb06998e411bbeed84e0f28c88262c0f","tid":145409,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:36:44.000Z","msg":"2018世界盃決賽周，揭幕戰於2018年6月14日晚舉行，不少人正思考俄羅斯如何解決足球流氓問題，俄國足總官員列別捷夫反其道而行，提議推動「Draka」把球迷打鬥合法化。他提議每方派出20人︰「俄羅斯將是這項新運動的先鋒。規則是作客球迷提出（打架），主隊球迷接受，約好時間在球場內舉行，不得有武器。」<br />\n<br />\n上限20人　不准用武器<br />\n<br />\n屬俄羅斯自由民主黨的列別捷夫去年歐國盃決賽周時，認為馬賽街頭打鬥沒有問題，並於twitter鼓勵球迷繼續，更視打鬥的球迷為真誠的支持者。他堅持俄羅斯有良好的警備可以控制場面：「我們有齊完備的法律，做足安全措施，所有旅客都無需懼怕前來俄羅斯去欣賞球賽。」俄羅斯總統普京當時曾質疑「200個俄羅斯球迷如何攻擊逾千英格蘭球迷」，後來承諾會在決賽周時打擊流氓生事。"},{"pid":"6d63ddb209ef3d1ff52d30c2fcd0d2f790e0e6dd","tid":145409,"uid":3358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0e930089d63c9943582e929e96402fd0c1a160","tid":145409,"uid":36014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:46:27.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ca30a96d24375d29e14b065a5de2e3f658e609","tid":145409,"uid":37586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:47:21.000Z","msg":"20人中有一個係普京<br />\n羸硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380a5eb3d4c96c8f4f41f43daa4fb3fcf25b2a21","tid":145409,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:49:47.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6ce06e3046113809cd760719b33731a65d2ccd","tid":145